    <p>
    This page allow to manage the ban of the members. You can delete them if neeeded, from the list below.
    <h4>Ban from </h4>
    <ul>So you have the choice to ban a member from :
        <li>his nickname</li>
        <li>his <acronym title="Internet Protocol">IP</acronym> address</li>
        <li>his email or domain name</li>
    </ul>
    <h4>Message</h4>
    <ul><li>Put a message that explain the reaeson of the ban to the member when this one will try to come on the forum.</li></ul>
    <h4>Expiry</h4>
    <ul><li>At least, put an expiry date of this ban, if no date is provided, the ban will stay definitely</li></ul>
